django-issueinspector installation
==================================


Python ``pip`` package is required to install ``django-issueinspector``.


From sources
------------

Use the following command line to install ``django-issueinspector`` from sources directory (containing setup.py):

    pip install .

or

    python setup.py install


From PyPI
---------

Alternatively you can install ``django-issueinspector`` from PyPI:

    pip install django-issueinspector


Use `-U` flag for upgrade:

    pip install -U django-issueinspector

